summary: The paper introduces EXABSUM, a novel Automatic Text Summarization (ATS) approach capable of generating extractive and abstractive summaries. It employs statistical and semantic scoring for extractive summarization and a graph-based method for abstractive summarization, demonstrating competitive performance on multi-domain benchmarks.
